<item>
            <title>[SEC-198] AccessDeniedException removes role visibility from authz:authorize tags</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-198</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;My application has a role dependent JSP elements, where roles are determined via the authz:authorize tags.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If a URL is hit that throws an AccessDeniedException (not a usual thing I guess, but still...), the user&apos;s roles are no longer visible to the authz:authorize tags.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;PS - I&apos;ll see if I can determine the cause and generate a patch.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>N/A</environment>
